    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《Passenger 23》是一款以在休息站工作的学生为主角的恐怖游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的第一个夜班即将开始，等待你的远比想象中更加可怕。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/f455306f2c2f18034a1d114b7d6a9176.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/f455306f2c2f18034a1d114b7d6a9176.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>过往痕迹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >23名乘客与一个黑暗的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/61060f8d639d2e28c65ce9a2fb607cc1.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/61060f8d639d2e28c65ce9a2fb607cc1.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>午夜访客</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >答案很黑暗，问题更黑暗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/bebab1b62628db87064f13ded4414937.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/bebab1b62628db87064f13ded4414937.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的轮班已经开始！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论深夜发生什么，你都必须继续售卖商品，保持环境整洁，并为前往洗手间的乘客继续出售代币。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/6732456840534fb033b1b31ece2ac10d.poster.avif?t=1741910468\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369810/extras/6732456840534fb033b1b31ece2ac10d.webm?t=1741910468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态剧情: </strong>随着时间的推移，紧张和秘密逐渐升级，原本平凡的夜班演变成致命的冒险。<strong><br>生存与探索: </strong>恢复电力，发现奇怪的笔记，并避开周围潜伏的威胁。<br><strong>紧张氛围: 沉浸在黑暗、孤独与诡异氛围交织的恐怖休息站之中。<br>真实故事改编: 随着一桩十年前事故的秘密浮现，你将直面正义的黑暗面。<br>复古画面: 享受PS1风格的低分辨率复古恐怖体验。<br>完整土耳其语和英语支持: 支持完整的土耳其语和英语内容，带来双语沉浸式体验。</strong></p>",
